Package: sample.design
Type: Package
Title: Generate Sample Designs for Assessment, Inventory, and Monitoring Projects
Date: 2020-12-08
Version: 0.6
Authors@R: c(person(given = c("Nelson", "G."), family = "Stauffer", email = "nelson.stauffer@ars.usda.gov", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Steve", "Garman", email = "sgarman@blm.gov", role = c("aut")))
Description: Creates spatially balanced sample designs using a generalized random tessellation stratified either from imported feature classes or the BLM/JER AIM master sample points.
